	* add --stop-callback-url called when recording is stopped
2006-07-17 Klaas Jan Wierenga   <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.3
	* unify log messages, add timestamp to log messages
	* prevent repeated output of same log message
	* added --version|-V option
	* fixed SEGV on closing output file when it wasn't opened in the first place
	* stricter checking on passed connect/reconnect options (should be >0)
	* enabled CURLOPT_FAILONERROR to prevent error ending up in mp3 output
	* better error message on unknown option

